title: FC Progresul Briceni
text:
FC Progresul Briceni was a Moldovan <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Briceni">Briceni</a>, Moldova. They played in the <a href="Moldovan%20National%20Division">Moldovan National Division</a>, the top division in Moldovan football.
History.
1992 – foundation as FC Vilia Briceni
1994 – renaming in FC Progresul Briceni
1996 – dissolution
